'''Cauliflower''' is a [[Vegetables|vegetable]] [[Crops|crop]] that grows from [[Cauliflower Seeds]] after 12 days. Cauliflower is one of only three crops that can grow into a [[Crops#Giant Crops|giant crop]].

==Stages==
Cauliflower can become a [[Crops#Giant Crops|Giant Crop]].
