==Tailoring==
Cauliflower is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create a dyeable {{name|Shirt159|link=Tailoring{{!}}Shirt And Belt|class=inline}}. It is a white dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed.

==Quests==
*[[Jodi]] will request a fresh cauliflower by mail on [[Spring]] 19th, for the [[Quests#Jodi's Request|"Jodi's Request" Quest]].  The reward is {{Price|350}} and 1 [[Friendship]] heart.
*Cauliflower may be randomly requested in [[Spring]] at the "Help Wanted" board outside [[Pierre's General Store]] for a reward of {{Price|525}} and 150 [[Friendship]] points.

